dc_title_s: PLSS Fond du Lac County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This point data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Fond_du_Lac_PLSS_2018.gdb.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation and online dataset download, please visit http://www.fdlco.wi.gov/departments/departments-f-m/land-information/data-download.
